<a href="/questions/251594-might-the-readers-enjoy-this-essay-on-the">Might the readers enjoy this essay on the historical accuracy of the book as a complement? http://www.columbia.edu/~hds2/learning/Learning_from_shogun_txt.pdf</a>
</div>
